  "page": "House Harlaw (disambiguation)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>Several houses from the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a> share the name <b>Harlaw</b>:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Harlaw\" title=\"House Harlaw\"><img alt=\"House Harlaw.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a6/House_Harlaw.svg/20px-House_Harlaw.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a6/House_Harlaw.svg/30px-House_Harlaw.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a6/House_Harlaw.svg/40px-House_Harlaw.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Harlaw\" title=\"House Harlaw\">House Harlaw</a> of Harlaw, one of the most powerful house on <a href=\"/index.php/Harlaw\" title=\"Harlaw\">Harlaw</a>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Harlaw_of_Grey_Garden\" title=\"House Harlaw of Grey Garden\"><img alt=\"House Harlaw of Grey Garden.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a8/House_Harlaw_of_Grey_Garden.svg/20px-House_Harlaw_of_Grey_Garden.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a8/House_Harlaw_of_Grey_Garden.svg/30px-House_Harlaw_of_Grey_Garden.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a8/House_Harlaw_of_Grey_Garden.svg/40px-House_Harlaw_of_Grey_Garden.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Harlaw_of_Grey_Garden\" title=\"House Harlaw of Grey Garden\">House Harlaw of Grey Garden</a>, a cadet branch</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Harlaw_of_Harlaw_Hall\" title=\"House Harlaw of Harlaw Hall\"><img alt=\"House Harlaw of Harlaw Hall.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d2/House_Harlaw_of_Harlaw_Hall.svg/20px-House_Harlaw_of_Harlaw_Hall.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d2/House_Harlaw_of_Harlaw_Hall.svg/30px-House_Harlaw_of_Harlaw_Hall.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d2/House_Harlaw_of_Harlaw_Hall.svg/40px-House_Harlaw_of_Harlaw_Hall.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Harlaw_of_Harlaw_Hall\" title=\"House Harlaw of Harlaw Hall\">House Harlaw of Harlaw Hall</a>, a cadet branch</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Harlaw_of_Harridan_